title: Spacious Studio Suite, Utilities & Laundry Included
posting_body: ['Spacious, studio suite in quiet, Inner Richmond home.', 'Nearest cross-streets are 2nd Avenue and Cabrillo.', 'Substantial living area, plus kitchen amenities and full bath (approx.', '750 sq.', 'ft. in all).', 'Good closet space.', 'Pergo/laminate flooring, no carpet.', 'Good windows and light.', 'Offered unfurnished.', 'Water, garbage, PG&E, and internet included.', 'Free laundry facilities (washer/dryer) also on site.', 'No parking provided.', 'Excellent access to multiple bus lines: 31, 38, 5.', 'Well-stocked local market within one block and supermarket five blocks away.', 'Variety of stores and restaurants within short walking distance.', 'One block to Golden Gate Park.', 'Available now.', '$2250/month for 1 occupant and $2300/month for 2 occupants, one year lease.', 'No more than 2 occupants allowed.', 'Non-smokers only.', 'No partying or drugs.', 'This is a quiet, friendly, family neighborhood.', 'Email brief description of yourself along with a contact phone number and whatever additional questions you have.']
